Some documents in this repository reference, quote, or discuss the work of other researchers, institutions, and organizations. Those works remain under their original licenses and copyrights. Algorapolis claims no ownership of third-party research; all such content is cited for scholarly reference and critical analysis under fair use / fair dealing principles.

